Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:11.82,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is not an all-powerful technique,\Nas one cannot create something out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:17.66,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to gain something,\None must present something of equal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:22.37,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,This is the concept of equivalent exchange, the fundamental basis of alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.96,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is a taboo in alchemy. Human transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.67,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,One must not commit this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about the rumors of the High Priest of Lior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He creates flowers out of nothingness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It could just be a sleight of hand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But if it isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:25.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It could be what we've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A heavenly stone that destroyed Xerxes overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:34.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The great elixir that had been sealed away by a sage from the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:39.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There are many names for it, but to put it simply, it is something that reinforces alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we had this, we could get your body back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why is this all that's written down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be great if it's the real stone this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, Al, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.37,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Scattering Daddy's studies again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.33,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no doodling on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doodling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's... alchemy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Did you learn that from Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How do we learn from someone who's not even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the books we read.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Was in the books...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Were we not supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You boys are amazing! As expected of Daddy's children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.48,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to brag to everyone about you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom praised us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because we liked that, we started getting into alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But... in the summer of that year...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:53.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom passed away due to an epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, too. Let's go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If Dad comes home-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's not our Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even come back for Mom's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we could bring Mom back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:31.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But one of the books said that\Ntransmutating humans isn't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So... We'll keep it between us, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.67,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:46.80,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma said that if you cry for someone who's passed away, that person grieves as much as you cried for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:57.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who cries all the time 'cause\Nyour parents are always gone and you're lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I was ever worried about you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.91,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,If you get home later than me, you don't get any supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that? Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.20,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.46,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, you have to drink your milk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I hate milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.46,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't drink it, you'll be a runt forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a runt, you midget hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.09,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! You pea-sized runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Minimum hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.59,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Micro runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're no bigger than an ant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.97,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,You're no bigger than a flea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.02,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You were reading your book in school again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.90,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay attention in class, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.48,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,So, what book were you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business, Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:49.78,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,That's no fair! You two always keep little secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:59.00,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed! Al! We're having stew tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The person who invented stew is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's milk in it, yet it tastes so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:14.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The fact they thought of adding milk to vegetable soup is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's important for scientists to drastically change their thinking sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:25.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Human transmutation probably needs something drastic like that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:31.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, we researched human transmutation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:38.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...and improved our abilities by training with\Nour alchemy master in order to revive our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It took many years, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to see Mom's smiling face again."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to live happily with Mom again."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,With those thoughts in our hearts, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Water, 35L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Carbon, 20kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ammonia, 4L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lime, 1.5kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Phosphorus, 800g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Salt, 250g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Niter, 100g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sulfur, 80g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Fluorine, 7.5g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Iron, 5g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Silicon, 3g.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's write the construction formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is the information about the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be... rebound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.59,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,BROTHER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:32.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thanks for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an existence that you folks like to call the "world".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the universe. In other words, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the "Truth". In other words, entirety.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, "one". And, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:48.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. I'm-an-idiot-who-acts-all-high-and-mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the "truth".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:26.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It was as though all of the information in the world was shoved directly into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! My head's gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being disassembled...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like my head was going to crack open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I suddenly realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is the "Truth".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,M... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.74,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:09.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There were no errors in my human transmutation theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm missing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I had gone a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I would've found what I was looking for; the truth to human transmutation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Show it to me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.51,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.81,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,I can only show you that much for that toll you've paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Toll?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.14,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.82,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Equivalent exchange, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.82,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Like I'd let this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This... This wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They took it away!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Help me... someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I wanted!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al... Alphonse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse! Alphonse!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... Dammit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back... He's my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it be an arm or a leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Or even my heart! You can take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So give him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's my only brother!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.62,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. You were still hangin' around in Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.87,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They're letting me return to Eastern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.75,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.88,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better at least be a Brigadier General the next time you come, all right, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You say that as if it's a walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.59,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, if you're going back,\NI'll go ahead and give this to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.55,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.89,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,It's the final report about Isaac McDougal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.06,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't seen it yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy from Xing? {Rentanjutsu - made up term; refers to Chinese Alchemy}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.36,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, something like that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.24,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I've got no idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.36,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No, never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.37,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how are the Elric brothers doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not their keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:57.04,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you have Ed become a State Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.21,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a kid, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.42,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're in the army,\Nyou will experience Hell someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.34,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Just like we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Hell, they've seen it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.98,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty of it, in fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.91,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Colonel, they're not in the backyard ei-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.79,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.21,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those Elric brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.96,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down, Den.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.84,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,To customers, you have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.68,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What business does a soldier have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I just came from your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is all that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What did you make?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Please forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry... We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.91,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:20.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was a talented alchemist, so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:25.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,To think that a child performed human transmutation, though it was incomplete,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,and even managed to affix a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:33.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He has more than enough to be a State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:40.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If he became a State Alchemist, he'd have to fight as a soldier during times of emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:45.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}At the same time, the position comes with many privileges, and they'd be allowed to perform research of the highest level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:50.24,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They may be able to discover\Na way to recover their bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:58.41,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,After these boys staggered in here\Ncovered in blood, I went to their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.96,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.38,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,That was not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.88,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Is alchemy what allowed them to create something horrible like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.43,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:14.01,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling these boys to look at Hell again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.39,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.02,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.94,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.11,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Riza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.65,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Riza Hawkeye. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.95,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Riza...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.33,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever shot somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.17,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.21,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:52.13,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mom and Dad were taken to a battlefield and killed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.81,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, you two are trying to take Ed and Al, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:02.44,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Whether they come or not is up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.31,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.98,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just presenting you with the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.57,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Whether they want to move forward or stay stuck in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:18.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you want to end your life in despair or bow down to the army, seeking what possibilities lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:21.33,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's those boys who have to make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:27.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If the possibility lies on that path, then you should move forward to return your body to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that path is a muddy river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.72,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you become a soldier, Ms. Riza?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.90,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have someone I want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.19,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.03,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.28,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is good-bye, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.29,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.83,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.79,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.42,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.05,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But his eyes looked spiritless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.05,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Those... were burning eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.52,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,You won't regret it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How long would it take for both the surgery and rehab?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.95,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say about three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,One year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.58,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be coughing up blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, put up with it for a little longer, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put you back in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But when that time comes,\Nyou're going to get your limbs back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Your body's all fixed up now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Just alchemy left to train now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since I haven't used it since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you haven't used it since you affixed my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:28.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:34.09,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Brother! You did it without a transmutation circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:37.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how our master does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, too, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:46.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,See... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No... never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.94,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You transformed my automail, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna transform my head instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Uncute machine freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.83,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care if I'm not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.33,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with being a machine freak, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:10.33,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to support you until you get your limbs back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite rare that you've decided to watch the exam, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:21.51,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I heard that a twelve year-old was being tested,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.64,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,so I just thought I'd drop by so I would have something to talk about with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.27,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, an arm made of steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I got it during the civil war in the west...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:35.02,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we sure had a lot of trouble with Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That's Führer President King Bradley!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.37,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let the examination begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:51.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something to draw a transmutation circle with?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.84,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Without a transmutation circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.90,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is quite something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:17.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...And some military figure may be assassinated like this, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You guys might want to think about changing this examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.42,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, he's certainly got a lot of pluck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.88,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't understand the size of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:52.14,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with the rest of your exams, young alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When did he draw his sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Brother is doing all right on the exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.11,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.99,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,If Ed becomes a State Alchemist...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.45,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,...will you be leaving this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.26,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the badge of a State Alchemist, the silver pocket watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:27.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your certificate and the agreements are... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.26,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President has given you quite the ironic title...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:33.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.94,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're now a dog of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I, Führer President King Bradley, hereby appoint...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:44.53,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...thou, Edward Elric, as a State Alchemist,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:47.20,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,and bestow thee with the title, "Fullmetal".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:49.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:54.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The second name that's given to all State Alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The name that you'll be carrying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.87,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,"Fullmetal Alchemist".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I like it. Sounds like something heavy to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:12.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lior, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There should be some clue there on how to get Al's body back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Philosopher's Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:06.09,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Ed and Al, arriving in the city of Lior, meet Cornello, a man who preaches the revival of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:09.13,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Pray and believe, and thou shall be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:14.51,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,As Cornello preached those words, he wore the bright, red, Philosopher's Stone on his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:19.10,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:21.77,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3, City of Heresy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:26.40,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,What, exactly, is the happiness that can be earned by turning away from reality? {way too long to fit in the time it has, no space to extend it into either, plz2shorten -F}
